    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I agree, we might not want to have beta changelog in the final one. But, I would appreciate to still have changes for the beta in a changelog.\r\n\r\nCan we try to have this flow for beta:\r\n\r\n* tag locally the beta\r\n* generate the changelog & update it\r\n* remove the tag locally\r\n\r\nAnd when we have a non-beta, re-generate the changelog from start so it removes the \"beta\" parts of it? What do you think?",
    "created_at": "2018-03-19T17:06:08Z",
